			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Nickel sulfate is a chemical compound that comes in the form of a salt. Typically, it is used in electroplating, as well as in the production of catalysts and as a precursor in the formulation of various chemicals. The production route involves the dissolution of nickel metal or nickel oxides in sulfuric acid. The quality of nickel sulfate can vary depending on its purity and water content (hexahydrate or anhydrous forms). It is generally available as a production mix at plant.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硫酸镍是一种盐类化合物。常用于电镀，催化剂制备以及作为各种化学品配方中的前体。其生产路线包括在硫酸中溶解镍金属或氧化镍。硫酸镍的质量可根据其纯度和含水量（六水合物或无水形式）而变化。一般以生产混合物的形式在工厂中提供。</common:generalComment>
